# Top K Frequent Elements

LINK - https://neetcode.io/problems/top-k-elements-in-list/question?list=neetcode150

```python
class Solution:
    def topKFrequent(self, nums: List[int], k: int) -> List[int]:
        return [num for num,freq in Counter(nums).most_common(k)]
        return [num for num,freq in Counter(nums).most_]
```

# Valid Anagram

Link - https://neetcode.io/problems/is-anagram/question?list=neetcode150

```python
class Solution:
    def isAnagram(self, s: str, t: str) -> bool:
         if len(s) != len(t):
            return False
         return Counter(s) == Counter(t)
```

# Encode and Decode Strings

Link - https://neetcode.io/problems/string-encode-and-decode/question?list=neetcode150

```python
class Solution:

    def encode(self, strs: List[str]) -> str:
        op = ""
        for s in strs:
            op+= str(len(s))+"#"+s
        return op
    def decode(self, s: str) -> List[str]:
        op = []
        while s:
            index = s.find("#")
            num = int(s[:index])
            num_string = s[index+1:index+num+1]
            op.append(num_string)
            s =s[num+index+1:]
        return op
```